The last few days have meant more to me than I think she will ever realize - I got to watch what felt like was me, 17 years ago. 

We learned that patience is our best friend, we gotta pick up our feet, follow close, and that sometimes it doesn’t always work out in our favor. And 17 years down the road there’s still more to learn. 

A very very special little girl that I would share a tree with in the turkey woods anytime, anywhere 🤍

A single season slam. 

Gas, time, money, sweat, an ungodly amount of redbull, PTO (sorta), sanity, and a whole lot of faith are what it consisted of, but if you know me, you know A it’s been a long time comin and B I’d do it all over again 100x in a row. The peak of my year, every year, is when a longbeards feet hit the ground as the suns hittin the trees. 

The turkey woods were the first ones I walked into as a kid, and I hope they’re the last ones I walk into when I’m old and grey — I’m not too sure if I have the right words for what this seasons meant to me but I guess that’s just that, it’s something I shared with me, myself, God, family, and the best friends you could ask for & there’s nothing I would of changed about it. 

Thank you Lord for the best season yet and plenty more to follow. Visit the link in @mallardbay_’s bio to hear about the whole season 🤞🏽

They always talk about “that dog a girl gets in her 20s”, but what they don’t talk about is the impact that little dog makes. 

When you’re 15 hours & some change away from most of the people that love you, that little dog makes all the difference.. 

She’s my bestfriend. My shadow. She’ll be shotgun in the truck (you sit your ass in the back). She’ll be on all the trips. “Is Kimber coming?” You bet. Would you rather fly or drive? “I’m driving, my hounds comin..” 

What a year it’s been sharing oxygen with this little 4 legged yella dog. I’m so excited for what we will do in our time on this earth together, Kimbo 

— Mama 

🐾

We haven’t had a surprise-free Christmas for quite some time now & I wouldn’t have it any other way — Our baby is givin’ us a baby 🫶🏽

No matter what, no matter why, no matter where, no matter who. I couldn’t love you more even if I tried!

50 cent once said “if it ain’t makin’ me money, makin’ me better, or makin’ me happy.. I ain’t got time for it” 

Large mood for ‘24 🤝
